jokes.title: Thief!
jokes.text: What do you call a thieving alligator? A Crookodile

jokes.title: Maybee I Will, Maybee I Won’t!
jokes.text: What do you call a bee that can’t make up its mind? A Maybe

jokes.title: HiYa!
jokes.text: What do you call a pig that does karate? Pork chop

jokes.title: Nursing Math
jokes.text: Never trust math teachers who use graph paper. They’re always plotting something.

jokes.title: Math Buddies
jokes.text: Q: What do you call friends who love math? A: algebros

jokes.title: Monkeying Around
jokes.text: Did you hear about the monkeys who shared an Amazon account? They were Prime mates.

jokes.title: Beef It Up
jokes.text: Don’t use “beef stew” as a computer password. It’s not stroganoff.

jokes.title: Balloon Music
jokes.text: What kind of music are balloons afraid of? Pop Music

jokes.title: Musical Snake
jokes.text: What is the musical part of a snake? The scales.

jokes.title: Duvet Cover
jokes.text: Me and my friends are in a band called “Duvet”. We’re a cover band.
